    The Raven allows you to easily communicate with other players.
Once summoned, the Raven will remain perched on your shoulder
until banished.

Commands:
  - summon raven:          Summons the Raven to you (costs 10 sp)
  - rt <player> <message>: Tells <player> <message> (costs 2  sp)
  - rloc <player>:         Finds <player>           (costs 30 sp)
  - rpeck <player>:        Pecks <player>           (no cost)
  - ban raven:             Banishes the Raven       (costs 10 sp)
